snippet.title: Dark Castle color version (Macintosh game 1994)
snippet.description:
It's a color remake of Dark Castle by Delta Tao Software.
The original game is developed by Silicon Beach Software, released for many platforms (Amiga, Apple IIGS, Atari ST, MS-DOS and so on).

It's very difficult to control the main player. (attack, jump and so on)
